messages.speech:
You are responsible for notifying the Access Center/Disability Services if the accommodations that have been provided do not meet your needs.
http://www.century.edu/support-services/assistive-services-century-college/disability-services
If you have attempted to resolve issues related to your accommodations, but you feel that Century College has failed to meet your needs you may file a complaint. Complaints generally are about issues such as:

 - accommodations provided
 - timely implementation of accommodations
 - access to buildings
 - access to information
